ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR EDUCATIONAL USE:

This project is part of "One App a Day" - a challenge focused on modern development
techniques, quality code, and building technical portfolios through community learning.

When using this project:
- ✅ You're encouraged to learn, modify, and share your improvements
- ✅ Community contributions and code reviews are welcome
- ✅ Share your learnings and improvements back with the community
- ✅ Use for commercial projects - but maintain attribution
- ✅ Create your own challenge following the same principles

Contributors:
- The code quality improvements come from collective learning
- Each app demonstrates techniques for the community to learn from
- Your improvements strengthen the challenge for everyone

Attribution requested (but not required):
If you use this project, please mention:
- "Based on One App a Day Challenge"
- Link to the original repo: https://github.com/Jodev97/OnedayOneapp
- The original author(s) if adapting specific apps

